trans-unit.source: To obtain the <xref:System.Reflection.MemberTypes> value for a type:
trans-unit.target: Para obter o <xref:System.Reflection.MemberTypes> valor para um tipo:

trans-unit.source: Get a <xref:System.Type> object that represents that type.
trans-unit.target: Obter um <xref:System.Type> objeto que representa o tipo.

trans-unit.source: Retrieve the value of the <xref:System.Type.MemberType%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.
trans-unit.target: Recuperar o valor da <xref:System.Type.MemberType%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: To get the <xref:System.Reflection.MemberTypes> values for the members of a type.:
trans-unit.target: Para obter o <xref:System.Reflection.MemberTypes> valores para os membros de um tipo.:

trans-unit.source: Get a <xref:System.Type> object that represents that type.
trans-unit.target: Obter um <xref:System.Type> objeto que representa o tipo.

trans-unit.source: Retrieve the <xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo> array that represents the members of that type by calling the <xref:System.Type.GetMembers%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method.
trans-unit.target: Recuperar o <xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo> matriz que representa os membros desse tipo chamando o <xref:System.Type.GetMembers%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> método.

trans-unit.source: Retrieve the value of the From the <xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo.MemberType%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property for each member in the array.
trans-unit.target: Recuperar o valor de From a <xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo.MemberType%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> propriedade para cada membro da matriz.

trans-unit.source: A `switch` statement in C# or `Select Case` statement in Visual Basic is typically used to process member types.
trans-unit.target: Um `switch` instrução em c# ou `Select Case` instrução no Visual Basic é normalmente usada para processar tipos de membro.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Reflection.MemberTypes> matches CorTypeAttr as defined in the corhdr.h file.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Reflection.MemberTypes> faz a correspondência de CorTypeAttr conforme definido no arquivo corhdr.
